                },
                "category": "defensive",
                "description": {
                    "value": "<p><strong>Trigger</strong> The marp takes damage from a melee Strike</p>\n<hr />\n<p><strong>Effect</strong> The marp drops any items held in their hands, then Climbs or Strides up to 15 feet.</p>"
